trans-unit.source: Identifies the types of connection points that a transformer supports.
Transformers are used to translate data between two Web Parts controls with incompatible connection points.
trans-unit.target: 轉換程式用來轉譯具有不相容的連接點的兩個 Web 組件控制項之間的資料。

trans-unit.source: Connection points are incompatible when they provide or consume data through different interfaces.
trans-unit.target: 在提供或取用資料，透過不同的介面時，連接點不相容。

trans-unit.source: For example, a provider implementing a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow> could not directly connect to a consumer expecting a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>.
trans-unit.target: 例如，提供者實作的型別提供者連接點<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>無法直接連接到接收的型別提供者連接點的取用者<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>。

trans-unit.source: Instead, a transformer must be used to connect the two connection points.
trans-unit.target: 相反地，必須使用轉換程式連接的兩個連接點。

trans-unit.source: A customized transformer can be created by deriving a class from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: 衍生的類別也可以建立自訂的轉換程式<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>類別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute> attribute is applied to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute>屬性套用至<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>類別。

trans-unit.source: It defines the type of provider connection point and the type of consumer connection point that a transformer supports.
trans-unit.target: 它會定義提供者連接點的類型和轉換程式支援的消費者連接點的類型。

trans-unit.source: The type of consumer and provider connection points supported by the transformer must match the connection points of the consumer and provider Web Parts controls for a connection to be made between the controls.
trans-unit.target: 消費者和提供者連接點支援的轉換程式型別必須符合建立控制項之間的連接消費者和提供者 Web 組件控制項的連接點。

trans-unit.source: At run time, the type of connection points that a particular transformer supports can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 在執行階段，支援特定的轉換程式的連接點的類型可以透過擷取<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates the use of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute> attribute with a customized <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute>具有自訂屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>類別。

trans-unit.source: The attribute indicates that the `RowToStringTransformer` class can transform a provider connection point of type `IWebPartRow` to a consumer connection point of type `IString`.
trans-unit.target: 此屬性會指出`RowToStringTransformer`類別可以將轉換的型別提供者連接點`IWebPartRow`類型的消費者連接點`IString`。

trans-unit.source: This code example is part of a larger example found in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class overview.
trans-unit.target: 這個程式碼範例是在中找到之較大範例的一部分<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>類別概觀。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the interface supported by the consumer connection point.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the interface supported by the provider connection point.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute" /> class.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.%23ctor%2A> constructor sets the consumer connection point type and the provider connection point type for the transformer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.%23ctor%2A>建構函式設定轉換的消費者連接點類型和提供者連接點類型。

trans-unit.source: These values can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A> property and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A> property, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 這些值可以透過擷取<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A>屬性和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A>屬性，分別。

trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute>具有自訂屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>類別。

trans-unit.source: The attribute indicates that the `RowToStringTransformer` class can transform a provider connection point of type `IWebPartRow` to a consumer connection point of type `IString`.
trans-unit.target: 此屬性會指出`RowToStringTransformer`類別可以將轉換的型別提供者連接點`IWebPartRow`類型的消費者連接點`IString`。

trans-unit.source: The type of transformer.
Returns the consumer type a transformer can accept on a connection point.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the consumer connection point.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> object and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A> method to determine whether the consumer type of the transformer matches the consumer connection point of the Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>物件和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>物件都會使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>方法，以判斷轉換程式的取用者型別是否符合 Web 組件控制項的消費者連接點。
